data.title: Overwatch League MVP Pro-Files: JJANU
data.description: In this Overwatch League MVP Pro-File we take a look at JJANU. Known for his consistent D.Va play, JJANU is the rock the Vancouver Titans' success is built upon. From eating ultimates with his Defense Matrix to landing massive Self-Destructs, there's no question as to why JJANU is a candidate for this season's Overwatch League MVP. data.title: Overwatch League MVP Pro-File: guxue
data.description: In this Overwatch League MVP Pro-File we go bananas for the best Winston in the League, guxue. Representing the Chinese scene, guxue made a name for himself at the Overwatch World Cup. Since joining the Overwatch League with the Hangzhou Spark, guxue has overcome the language barriers to establish his team as one of the best in the league. data.title: Overwatch League MVP Pro-Files: sinatraa
data.description: In this Overwatch League MVP Pro-File we're talking all about sinatraa. Signed to the San Francisco Shock before he was old enough to play, sinatraa was originally known for his Tracer. As the meta shifted, sinatraa proved he was the real deal by easily transitioning to playing Zarya, quickly becoming one of the best in the League.
